This Thai basil beef (Pad Gra Prow) is one of the popular Thai street foods and takes only 20 minutes to prepare. You can use steak beef or ground beef, and quickly stir fry with aromatic Thai basil. With this recipe, you can taste a classic Thai food easily at home.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in smart.bio @beyondkimchee⁣
https://www.beyondkimchee.com/thai-beef-and-basil-stir-fry/⁣
⁣
태국바질이 들어간 소고기볶음..⁣
간단하게 후다닥 볶아서 고슬고슬한 자스민밥이랑 같이 드셔보세요. 태국의 맛이 그대로 전해집니다.⁣
⁣
⁣

You cam make this Korean tofu within 15 minutes with only a handful of ingredients that you might already have in your kitchen.⁣
⁣
It goes well with rice, noodles or porridge, and makes a perfect vegetarian dish if you use water instead of stock.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
두부 한모에서 나오는 근사한 맛!⁣
두부조림 반찬 하나만 있어도 밥한공기는 게눈 감추듯 사라지네요.⁣
⁣
⁣

Now you can make the best homemade spaghetti sauce with this easy recipe. Perfectly thick and packed with flavor, it is great for freezing or canning to plan for home cooked meals ahead of time. What makes this sauce amazing? Discover the secret ingredient here. This recipe makes a big batch.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
남다른 비법이 숨어있는 스파게티소스 레시피!⁣
2시간 이상 졸여주어야 제맛이 나는지라 만들때 크지막하게 한솥 준비하세요. ⁣
⁣
냉동하기도 좋아 두고두고 먹을수있어요.⁣
울집에선 제가 한며칠 여행갈일이 생기면 카레대신 요 스파게티소스를 냉동실에 쟁여놓고 갑니다. 그럼 가족들 끼니걱정이 덜해요. 😁😅⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣

Bulgogi hot pot (Jeongol) is a Korean beef hot pot dish with marinated bulgogi meat, a variety of vegetables, and glass noodles in a savory and slightly sweet broth. Typically served during cold winter months, this hearty, comforting Korean hot pot recipe is perfect for gatherings with family and friends.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
https://www.beyondkimchee.com/bulgogi-hotpot/⁣
⁣
쌀쌀해진 날씨엔 뜨끈한 소고기전골로 몸과 마음을 녹여봅니다.⁣
한냄비 수북히 채워 온가족이랑 둘러앉아 먹는맛이란...⁣
요런게 행복인거 같아요.⁣
⁣
⁣

Dried pollock soup (bugeo-guk) is a well known light hangover soup served as a breakfast in Korea. Shredded dried pollock fish is simmered with soybean sprouts and tofu in a flavorful stock. It is a quick and easy soup to fix within 15 minutes.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
국물맛 좋고 아삭아삭 씹히는 콩나물도 좋은 아침 북어해장국~!⁣
15분이면 간단하게 해결하는 레시피랍니다.⁣
⁣
⁣

Crispy crab cakes are irresistible! Impress yourself and your guests with these crispy Thai crab cakes with quick sriracha mayo and homemade sweet chili sauce. The addition of small amount of shrimp will enhance the texture of the crab cakes. ⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣

바삭한 크랩케잌은 거부하기 힘든 매력이 있죠.⁣
태국식 크랩케잌입니다.⁣
통조림게살에 다진새우 조금 넣어서 빵가루 묻혀 구워놓으면 귀신이 잡아가도 모를맛!⁣
⁣
스리라차 마요네즈나 스윗칠리소스에 찍어먹음 두말 필요없음!⁣

⁣

Korean sauna eggs are a popular Korean snack found in Korean spas or saunas. The eggs have a nutty, roasted flavor, and they are very satisfying to serve as a snack or breakfast. An Instant pot is the perfect cooking tool to make them at home easily.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in smart.bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
찜질방이 그리운 요즘... ⁣
인스턴트팟으로 찜질방달걀을 흉내내 봅니다. ㅎㅎ⁣

Apple brownies (aka apple blondies) are a satisfying sweet treat. Get your apple fix with this chewy yet cakey dessert that is chock full of apple and walnut. Spiced with cinnamon, this family friendly apple brownie recipe is a surprisingly great twist on traditional brownies.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
사과브라우니 드셔보셨어요?⁣
말 그대로 사과로 브라우니처럼 만드는건데...⁣
⁣
상큼한 사과에 은은한 계피향의 조화, 거기다 부드러우면서도 촉촉한 식감까지...⁣
가을에 �너무 잘어울리는 달달구리죠. 정말 쉬운 레시피여서 꼭 만들어보시길 바래요.⁣
⁣

This puff pastry apple strudel recipe is quick and easy. The recipe will teach you how to make classic German apple strudel with a store-bought puff pastry, apple, walnut, cinnamon in step-by-step instructions. ⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
요맘때 만들어드시면 최고인 사과스트루덜 입니다.⁣
퍼프 페이스트리 생지만 있다면 만드는건 식은죽먹기에요.⁣
만들어드신분들은 동서남북을 통해 모두 엄지척~ 해주셨던 레시피랍니다. ㅎㅎ⁣

How about enjoying this crunchy Taiwanese popcorn chicken for weekend movie night with your family?⁣
⁣
The crunchy bite size chicken pieces are tossed with fried basil and dusted with savory seasoning powder. Super satisfying!⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
대만 야시장에 가면 흔하게 보이는 대만식 팝콘치킨!⁣
입안에 넣으면 파삭파삭 식감과 더불어 짭쪼롬하면서 향기로운 감칠맛 때문에 손을 떼기가 어렵죠.⁣
대만에 살때 가끔 사먹었더랬는데... 옛추억 돋네요. 😋⁣
⁣
⁣

Learn how to prepare authentic Korean bibimbap at home, a dish of rice with sautéed vegetables, bulgogi beef (Korean BBQ ground beef), topped with a fried egg. This detailed post is full of tips and tricks, a list of tools, and recipe variations for making a bibimbap bowl in under 1 hour, and includes a simple way for making homemade red bibimbap sauce.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
https://www.beyondkimchee.com/bibimbap/⁣
⁣
⁣
비빔밥 1시간안에 만들기!⁣
구색맞고 간지나는 비빔밥을 1시간안에 만들어보세요. 후다닥 만들기 좋은 레시피랍니다.⁣
후라이팬으로 돌솥비빔밥 흉내도 낼수 있답니다. 😘⁣
⁣
⁣

How about crispy yet juicy beef for dinner? This Chinese crispy beef is a restaurant-quality recipe featuring super crispy strips of beef smothered in a sweet tangy glaze. Easy to prepare and loaded with flavor, your Asian dinner will be ready in just 30 minutes.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
중국식당에서 가장 인기있는 메뉴! 크리스피비프입니다.⁣
바삭하면서도 쫀득한 소고기맛에 새콤매콤달콤한 소스가 어우러지면 밥한공기쯤이여 쑥딱~이죠.⁣
중국식당 갈필요없이 집에서 30분만 투자하세요. 훨씬더 깔끔하고 맛깔지게 만들수있답니다.⁣
⁣
⁣

This classic doenjang jjigae recipe uses fermented Korean soybean paste to create a deeply flavorful stew accented with tofu and fresh vegetables. My step-by-step photos make at home preparation of the stew easy.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
보글보글~ 끓어오르는 된장찌개 뚝배기만 쳐다보기만 해도 돌아가신 친정엄마생각이 납니다.⁣

When the weather outside is chilling, nothing is more soothing than having a bowl of soup to warm you up. And you know that Korean cuisine is big on soups (and stews, too), right?⁣
⁣
You will love the collection of these homestyle Korean soup recipes. They are easy to prepare and just perfect for the winter season. ⁣
⁣
Get the recipes on smart.bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
추운 날씨에는 따끈한 국한그릇이면 몸을 편안하게 데워주는것 같아요. 한국요리에 빠질수없는 중요한 국 레시피 20개를 모아보았습니다.⁣
⁣
⁣

If you are looking for a quick, light meal under 15 minutes, this sesame soba noodle recipe makes a terrific weeknight dinner. Topped with crumbled seaweed and fried dumplings, you’ll have a hassle-free simple soba noodle bowl that everyone will love.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
바쁜 주중, 후다닥 만들어 먹을수있는 초간단하면서 맛있는 레시피를 원하신다면 매밀국수 볶음 어떠세요?⁣

15분 투자하셔서 냉동만두 구워 같이 드시면 가벼우면서도 든든하게 한끼 해결납니다.⁣
⁣
⁣

⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣

김가루 뿌려 같이 먹으면 별미입니다.⁣

This braised spicy Korean mackerel and radish (godeungeo jorim) recipe is a beloved Korean fish dish. The step-by-step instructions and cooking tips will help you to cook this delicious fresh mackerel without the worry of fish odor.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
저에게 고등어 무조림의 제일 하이라이트는 무!⁣
짭쪼롬하니 간이 딱 베인 물컹한 무조림이에 비린맛 없는 고등어살~⁣
밥한공기 거뜬히 비울수있어요. ⁣

This soondubu jjigae recipe is made with fresh soon tofu (also known as soft tofu or silken tofu), kimchi, and seafood. This popular spicy Korean soft tofu soup is quick and easy to fix within 30 minutes. Use any seafood of your choice for this recipe.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
조개랑 통새우 넣고 칼칼한 순두부찌개 한솥 끓여놓으니 밥도둑이 따로 없네요.⁣
역시 한국음식이 최고~! 👍⁣

These Swedish dream cookies, known as drömmar, are traditional buttery sugar cookies widely eaten in Sweden and other Scandinavian countries. A special ingredient (baker’s ammonia) makes these cookies airy crisp with a cracked surface. They melt in your mouth when you eat them.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in profile @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣

쫘악~ 갈라진 표면또한 멋집니다. 비밀의 재료가 있지요.⁣
몇개 안되는 재료로 아주 손쉽게 북유럽 쿠키의 맛을 즐겨보세요.⁣
⁣
⁣

This Spam fried rice with egg is a quick and easy way to use up leftover rice. In less than 20 minutes, crispy pan-fried Spam, fluffy eggs, and simple vegetables combine to create a quick and delicious weeknight meal that the whole family will love!⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
스팸으로 만들어본 볶음밥..⁣

This coffee-free variation of classic tiramisu is kid-friendly and great for those who cannot have coffee or alcohol! Using ground roast barley mimics the flavor of coffee, and this recipe makes it just as delicious as traditional tiramisu.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣
⁣
커피가 들어가지않는 맛있는 티라미수!⁣
이태리에서는 커피를 마시지못하는 사람들을 위한 대용으로 구운 보리를 갈아서 커피대용으로 마신다고 하죠. 맛을 보면 커피랑 비슷할거에요. ⁣
⁣
이 보리커피를 이용해 티라미수를 만들면 아이들에게도 카페인 염려없이 안심하고 먹일수있는 멋진 디저트가 완성됩니다. 만들기도 상당히 쉬워요. 시도해보시겠어요?⁣
⁣
⁣

Bulgogi beef takes on cheesesteak! This fantastic Korean fusion Philly cheesesteak style sandwich is packed with flavor and texture. It’s a simple and quick sandwich that takes 15 minutes — no need to marinate the bulgogi beef at all.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in bio @beyondkimchee⁣

불고기를 양념에 재우지않고 빠르고 간편하게 볶아서 치즈랑 함께 후다닥~ �샌드위치로 만들어보세요.⁣
⁣
15분 정도 투자하시면 색다르면서도 넘 맛있는 퓨전요리가 완성된답니다.⁣

What is your favorite baking recipe for the holiday? It's hard for me to pick just one but this Finnish cardamom bread (Pulla) is one I make every year. The braided look of this sweet bread recipe makes a stunning treat for the holidays, whether for breakfast or for afternoon tea. The delightful cardamom scent really warms the soul during the winter holidays.⁣
⁣
Recipe link in smart.bio @beyondkimchee⁣
